title: Fearless (Taylor's Version) (Song)
description:
What is the true meaning behind Taylor Swift's song Fearless? Are there any noticeable differences in Taylor's version?
Ana, Amy, Lacey and Nick rediscover (and some, discover for the first time) the true magic behind Fearless... and it's a wonderful way to kick off the start of the Fearless era.. Taylor's version!
